Are you enjoying your time on the server?

Would you like to help contribute to the server and get a few perks for it?

If you donate $50 USD or more, then you will get the Purple Supporter rank. This grants you a purple name in chat, some more chunk claims and the knowledge that you helped keep the server running by helping pay for the electricity costs, Internet bill and hardware upgrade/fix costs.

You also get access to the trashcan (icon in inventory) and /trash_can command. Yay?

Thank you for supporting us.
